checkwin()
this function checks for all the scenarios for a win to occur and returns value accordingly.
1 FOR GAME IS OVER WITH RESULT
this occurs when we have 3 boxes with one symbol.
-1 FOR GAME IS IN PROGRESS
this occurs when not all the boxes are filled.
O GAME IS OVER AND NO RESULT
this occurs when all the boxes are filled and there are no 3 consecutive symbols of the same kind.

the player chances are choses by a incrimenting player variable and for all the even outcomes the 2nd player plays thier turn.

the square array keeps track of all the valus on the board

